				<li style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; list-style-position:inside; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">无追索权供应链融资：是指融资申请人通过本平台向资金方转让其持有的以</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">东风金融-创格</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">为凭证的应收账款，并发起融资申请，资金方为融资申请人提供的无追索权供应链融资服务。</span></li>
