				<li style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; list-style-position:inside; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">核心企业：指已完成平台注册的在产业链中被公认的优势企业。该企业为了巩固其产业链发展，优化产业、提升产业的竞争力等，组织其上下游企业建设供应链金融体系，提供更加优质便捷的供应链金融服务。</span></li>
				<li style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; list-style-position:inside; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">兑付</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">日：指根据</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">东风金融-创格</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">记载信息，开单人履行</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">东风金融-创格</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">偿付义务，持单人获取</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">东风金融-创格</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">偿付款项的日期。</span></li>
